<subsection name="Generate Elasticsearch schema from PDS data dictionary" id="GenSchema">
<p>
To generate Elasticsearch schema from a PDS data dictionary, run <i>generate-schema</i> command:
</p>

<p>
<source>
Usage: registry-manager generate-schema &lt;options&gt;

Generate Elasticsearch schema from one or more PDS data dictionaries.

Required parameters:
  -config &lt;path&gt;  Configuration file.
Optional parameters:
  -file &lt;path&gt;    Output file for Elasticsearch schema file. Default value is '/tmp/registry/schema.json'.
</source>
</p>

<p>
This command is described in <a href="reg-custom.html">Registry Customization</a> section.
</p>

</subsection>

