<subsection name="Update Elasticsearch schema from PDS data dictionary" id="UpdateSchema">
<p>
To update Elasticsearch schema from a PDS data dictionary, run <i>update-schema</i> command:
</p>

<p>
<source>
Usage: registry-manager update-schema &lt;options&gt;

Update Elasticsearch schema from one or more PDS data dictionaries.

Required parameters:
  -config &lt;path&gt;   Configuration file.
Optional parameters:
  -auth &lt;file&gt;     Authentication config file
  -es &lt;url&gt;        Elasticsearch URL. Default is http://localhost:9200
  -index &lt;name&gt;    Elasticsearch index name. Default is 'registry'
</source>
</p>

<p>
This command is described in <a href="reg-custom.html">Registry Customization</a> section.
</p>

